headline: AeroVironment Boosts Profit Outlook After Revenue More Than Doubles
summary: The defense contractor said it now expects adjusted earnings per share of $3.60 to $3.70 for the current fiscal year, up from its prior outlook of $2.80 to $3.00.

headline: A Fresh Look at FactSet Research Systems (FDS): Valuation After Wells Fargo’s Price Target Cut
summary: FactSet Research Systems just got a fresh look from Wall Street, and it is the kind that makes investors sit up and pay attention. Wells Fargo reaffirmed its Underweight rating on the stock, but the real headline is their decision to lower the price target by 12%. Moves like this by major analysts can leave investors wondering whether market expectations are shifting for FactSet and what that means for the company’s future trajectory.
